import React from 'react'; import { Typography, TableContainer, Table, TableRow, TableCell, Paper, Box, Link } from '@mui/material'; const BasicStats = ({ data }) => { return ( Basic Statistics Sector: {data.sector} Industry: {data.industry} Exchange: {data.exchange} Country: {data.country_name} ISIN: {data.isin} Primary Ticker: {data.primary_ticker} Fiscal Year End: {data.fiscal_year_end} Web URL: Link
